public Vtiful\Kernel\ConditionalFormat Vtiful\Kernel\ConditionalFormat::maximumRule intvalue
Sets the rule type used to interpret the maximum value of a color scale or data bar conditional format, using one of the Vtiful\Kernel\ConditionalFormat::RULE_* constants.

&reftitle.parameters;


  value

   One of the Vtiful\Kernel\ConditionalFormat::RULE_* rule type constants that defines how the maximum value is evaluated.
